snippet.title: Space Jam Trailer 1996
snippet.description:
Space Jam Trailer 1996

Official Content From Acclaim

It's the looniest, high flyingest, most madcap basketball game ever! Join Michael (Air) Jordan, Bugs Bunny, Daffy Duck, and the rest of the Looney Tunes gang as they take on the 'Monstars' in slammin', jammin', intergalactic 3-on-3 action!
Platforms: Sega Saturn, Sony PlayStation

Sega Saturn, Sony PlayStation
